Rating: 4
Exceptional bread. Modifications: 2 tsp salt. 1/2 cup buttermilk and 2 cups water (instead of 2 1/2 cups water), I didn't have oatmeal, so I used 3/4 cup pinhead oatmeal, and 3/4 raisin bran minus the raisins. It's wonderful and hearty. I always use a high gluten flour like King Aurther's to make it nice and soft. Try it!

